#: ../content/installation.rst:44 ../content/updating.rst:69
msgid ""
"You can obtain either ``otrs-x.y.z.tar.gz`` or ``otrs-x.y.z.tar.bz2``. "
"Unpack the source archive (for example, using ``tar``) into the directory "
