msgid "``Ticket::SearchIndex::IndexArchivedTickets``"
msgstr "``Ticket::SearchIndex::IndexArchivedTickets``"

#: ../content/performance-tuning.rst:41
msgid ""
"Defines if archived tickets will be included in the search index (not "
